~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : ignall                                    ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : ignall

   This is a toggle that lets you listen or not to the conversation 
   in the room and any shouts and tells. Basically you ignore 
   everything. This is usefull if you want to read your mail or the 
   message boards and you dont want any speech appearing between pages.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : ignshout, igntell, ignore, unignore, showignore
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
